{"tid":790141,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[第一次] 韓文旅遊用語班","createTime":"2018-08-22T18:33:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T11:11:49.000Z","uid":175564,"like":10,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1d3999bf0b3e9bb60cf9b18d588f14d0052bedc5","tid":790141,"uid":175564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-22T18:33:27.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲打好,我又出現了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今次唔再係玩日文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩下其他語言。我地請到一位韓文老師肯教韓文。<br />\n主要係教旅遊用語,令大家去韓國時暢通無阻,當然都係入門級。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起我底都知道我地之前都搞過好多次活動,非搵食,係健康嘅。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為個韓文老師係出面請翻黎,所以要每人收翻$20<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得閒無野做放工可以黎join下~<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finterest.link/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinterest.link%2F&d=UXiOY3FKI0g2n2J%2FpP%2B8vP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0c34c8a0\" target=\"_blank\">https://finterest.link/</a><br />\n<br />\n點樣reg ac 報名 可以參考返上個post<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/782923/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/782923/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外我地個網都想比咁多位想搞活動嘅巴絲用得。自己有技能,唔係幾識搞活動,都可以搵我地幫手。例如租場地,helper等。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我地亦都會同ngo傾下合作,睇下ngo 肯唔肯放埋佢地嘅活動,令到個網更多元化。而ngo 開post 都會show 翻果間ngo 嘅icon。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最近見到都有巴絲係個網開活動,最好填返清楚d資料。活動目的,人數,地點,時間等<br />\n因為我地仲未整到waiting list 功能,所以麻煩大家最好講定預幾多人,然後開多d位。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記得唔好惡意收集他人資料。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/021151_8ad032a260e0be3d0a4aab6df07e3b7f.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F021151_8ad032a260e0be3d0a4aab6df07e3b7f.JPG&h=7bd496dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當人地報左名之後,tg/email 就會有果位參加者自己填嘅聯絡資料。<br />\n好似咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/021558_0e18c48ee64783302204fc6fa444ee00.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F021558_0e18c48ee64783302204fc6fa444ee00.jpeg&h=15464311&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家仲係小試牛刀,test 緊嘅階段,遲下有多d活動就會開po 宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46b674a772f4ad64ddaf895abe55a5cc6551f8b","tid":790141,"uid":100545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T00:48:55.000Z","msg":"過左25係咪唔報得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c4dfb951457567be0eaf728c64ea708e39a7f1","tid":790141,"uid":175564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d46b674a772f4ad64ddaf895abe55a5cc6551f8b","tid":790141,"uid":100545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T00:48:55.000Z","msg":"過左25係咪唔報得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T01:52:39.000Z","msg":"可以照報住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"859bb6814327bca0bc6f203487ae2500fba942f0","tid":790141,"uid":74908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:20:56.000Z","msg":"免費體驗但$20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f51fafd0369d6cfec2b7fed178186111236ec1b","tid":790141,"uid":81268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:44:45.000Z","msg":"睇落又幾正喎"},{"pid":"b07276a86dfba90b5e4dfe6f2dbb83c6f5cf4a49","tid":790141,"uid":175564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"859bb6814327bca0bc6f203487ae2500fba942f0","tid":790141,"uid":74908,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T02:20:56.000Z","msg":"免費體驗但$20<i